Position Measurement Analysis Tool
Interactive GUI for analyzing repeatability measurements from CSV files.

Position Measurement Analysis Tool
Interactive GUI for analyzing repeatability measurements from CSV files.
V3 - New feature in this version:
    1. Seperate analysis for foward and backward direction.
    2. load bunch of files and do the analysis for all file automaticlly.
    3. Load bunch mode - analysis range according to user definition.
    4. trend removal (linear or Polinomial)

V4.1 - 
